{"parse":{"title":"Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Four (TCG)","pageid":302976,"wikitext":{"*":"{{ExpansionPrevNext | prev=Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Three | next=Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Five }}\n{{TCGPromoInfobox\n|setname=Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Four\n|logo=Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Four logo.png\n|symbol=no\n|cards=86\n|period=February 14, 2024\n}}\n\n'''Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Four''' is a series of promotional cards released on February 14, 2024 through [[Play! Pok\u00e9mon|Pok\u00e9mon Organized Play]] events or affiliated products. This set features 86 specifically selected cards from the {{TCG|Lost Origin}} expansion through {{TCG|Obsidian Flames}}, in addition to {{TCG|SVE Basic Energies|SVE prints}} of {{TCG|Energy card|Basic Energy cards}}. All cards retained their original set number, but are marked with the Play! Pok\u00e9mon logo. Each Booster pack contains 6 cards. Foil cards in this set have Cosmos Holofoil except for {{TCG|Pok\u00e9mon V}} {{TCG|Pok\u00e9mon V|Pok\u00e9mon VMAX}}, {{TCG|Pok\u00e9mon V|Pok\u00e9mon VSTAR}} and {{TCG|Pok\u00e9mon ex}} which retain their regular foil patterns.\n\n==Card list==\n{{Setlist/header|title=Play! Pok\u00e9mon Prize Pack Series Four|bordercol={{Tcg grass color}}|tablecol={{Tcg fire color}}|cellcol={{Tcg water color}}|textcolor=000000|rarity=yes|symbol=no|promo=yes}}\n{{Setlist/entry|[[Image:SetSymbolLost Origin.png|18px|link=Lost Origin (TCG)]] 130/196|F|[[Giratina V (Lost Origin 130)|Giratina]]{{TCGV}}|Dragon||Ultra-Rare Rare|Standard Set Foil}}\n{{Setlist/entry|[[Image:SetSymbolLost Origin.png|18px|link=Lost Origin (TCG)]] 131/196|F|[[Giratina VSTAR (Lost Origin 131)|Giratina]]{{VSTAR}}|Dragon||Rare VSTAR|Standard Set Foil}}\n{{Setlist/entry|[[Image:SetSymbolLost Origin.png|18px|link=Lost Origin (TCG)]] 135/196|F|[[Hisuian Goodra V (Lost Origin 135)|Hisuian Goodra]]{{TCGV}}|Dragon||Ultra-Rare Rare|Standard Set Foil}}\n{{Setlist/entry|[[Image:Se